ent-BaseWeaponSniper = Снайперская Винтовка
    .desc = A rooty tooty point and shooty.
ent-WeaponSniperMosin = «Мосинка»
    .desc = A weapon of the masses, a true relic. The Kardashev-Mosin has served in nearly every armed conflict since its creation 670 years ago. The bolt-action design of the rifle remains virtually identical to its original design, whether used for hunting, sniping, or endless trench warfare. Uses .45 magnum ammo.
ent-WeaponSniperHristov = «Христов»
    .desc = For when you absolutely, positively need to make someone regret their life choices from a safe distance. Uses .60 anti-materiel ammo.
ent-Musket = мушкет
    .desc = This should've been in a museum long before you were born. Uses .60 anti-materiel ammo.
ent-WeaponPistolFlintlock = кремневый пистолет
    .desc = A pirate's companion. Yarrr! Uses .45 magnum ammo.
ent-WeaponPistolFlintlockEmpty = { ent-WeaponPistolFlintlock }
    .suffix = Empty
    .desc = { ent-WeaponPistolFlintlock.desc }
